<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Space Odyssey - Quantum Realm</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/images/quantum-realm-logo.png" alt="Quantum Realm Logo">
        </div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/areas">Explore Areas</a>
            <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="/offers">View Offers</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="space-odyssey-container">
        <h1 class="space-odyssey-title">Space Odyssey</h1>
        <p class="space-odyssey-text">Embark on an interstellar journey through the cosmos in the Space Odyssey zone. Discover alien worlds, dodge asteroid fields, and explore the mysteries of the universe.</p>

        <div class="space-odyssey-grid">
            <div class="space-odyssey-attraction">
                <img src="/images/attraction-1.jpg" alt="Alien Planet">
                <h3>Alien Planet</h3>
                <p>Visit an alien world with strange landscapes and extraterrestrial life.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-odyssey-attraction">
                <img src="/images/attraction-2.jpg" alt="Asteroid Belt">
                <h3>Asteroid Belt</h3>
                <p>Navigate through a treacherous asteroid belt filled with space debris and hidden dangers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-odyssey-attraction">
                <img src="/images/attraction-3.jpg" alt="Starship Adventure">
                <h3>Starship Adventure</h3>
                <p>Pilot your own starship on a mission to the far reaches of the galaxy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-odyssey-attraction">
                <img src="/images/attraction-4.jpg" alt="Galactic Warzone">
                <h3>Galactic Warzone</h3>
                <p>Experience the thrill of space combat in a high-stakes galactic battle.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-odyssey-book">
            <a href="/booking" class="btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Quantum Realm. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>Follow us: <a href="#">Facebook</a> | <a href="#">Instagram</a> | <a href="#">Twitter</a></p>
